# Frontend build-time configuration for SPROW LeadSphere.
# Copy to .env and set the deployed Scrapling API URL to enable live research.
# When empty, the frontend stays in demo mode (fictional sample leads).
#
# Vite inlines this at BUILD time, so it must also be set as a build variable
# in Cloudflare (Worker -> Settings -> Build -> Variables) before `npm run build`.
VITE_API_URL=
